<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.172658>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 14. Morphological aspects of Agalliota species. (10) A. dentata Oman, crown, pronotum and mesonotum; (11) A. scutaria Oman, genital capsule, lateral view; (12) A. parma Oman, genital capsule, lateral view; (13) A. vetusta Dutra & Egler, apical portion of aedeagus, dorsal view; (14) A. parallela Oman, apical portion of aedeagus, dorsal view. Figure 13 redrawn from Dutra & Egler (1982), remaining ones from Oman (1938)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/172658/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

